            <title>[DERBY-6477] OutOfMemoryError selecting from SYS.SYSALIASES</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-6477</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following query raises an OutOfMemoryError:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if&amp;gt; select a.alias, a.aliastype&lt;br/&gt;
from sys.sysaliases a&lt;br/&gt;
where a.javaclassname like &apos;org.apache.derby.catalog.SystemProcedures%&apos;;&lt;br/&gt;
ERROR XJ001: Java exception: &apos;Requested array size exceeds VM limit: java.lang.OutOfMemoryError&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
